'''Tranny chaser''' is a pejorative phrase usually applied to non-transgendered men who are sexually attracted to pre- or non-operative (penis intact) [[transwomen]]. Tranny Chasers generally do not fetishize post-operative transsexual women.

See also [[Homosexuality and transgender]] for more information on the difficulty in defining relationships involving transgendered people as [[homosexuality|homosexual]] or [[heterosexuality|heterosexual]].

